      "rationale": "Stiffness: FEA 312 N/mm vs. mean experimental 308 N/mm (1.3% diff, E/uval=0.41). Yield force: FEA 1842 N vs. mean 1819 N (1.3% diff, E/uval=0.38). Force at 40 mm: FEA 2104 N vs. mean 2089 N (0.7% diff, E/uval=0.22). All three QoIs satisfy both acceptance criteria across both laboratories."
